-- GM tumbles on report it won't make debt payment
-- 
-- Wed Apr 22, 2009 2:21pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/04/22/us-markets-stocks-gm-sb-idUSTRE53L53G20090422

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of General Motors Corp ( GM.N ) slid more than 5 percent to $1.61 -- a session low -- on the New York Stock Exchange after the Wall Street Journal reported that the beleaguered U.S. automaker will not make a June 1 debt payment of $1 billion. 

 (Reporting by  Ellis Mnyandu )